const colors = {

    greeny: "#A7C900",
    orangey: "#FFB400",
    grey: "#444444",
    lightgrey: "#D9D9D9",
    lightbluey: "rgba(0, 146, 255, 0.62)",
    lighterbluey: "rgba(0, 146, 255, 0.3)",
    lightorangey: "#FFDE8E",
    lightdarkgrey: "#333333",
    fadedgreeny: "#B9C57F",
    fadedbluey: "#A1D7FF",
